						<h3 class="entry-title">
				<a href="//lens.blogs.nytimes.com/2012/09/28/pictures-of-the-day-nepal-and-elsewhere-3/" rel="bookmark"
				   title="Permanent Link to Pictures of the Day: Nepal and Elsewhere">
					Pictures of the Day: Nepal and Elsewhere				</a>
